  m_text: "On your turn, you must play a card that is equal to or higher in value
    than the last card played. If you can\u2019t play a card, you will need to either
    draw a chance card from the deck or pick up the entire pile.\n\nIf you have multiple
    of the same card you can either place that or those cards or end your turn if
    you want to save those cards for later."
