      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'The first player to get rid of all their cards wins! The game continues
    until only one player has cards left. That player is the "Skitgubbe" (the loser).


    But
    the game can not be won if your last card is an Ace, 2 or a 10. If it is, you
    will pick up the cards in the pile and continue playing.


'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
