  m_text: "Each player has three face-down cards and three face-up cards placed on
    top of them. You can only play the face-up cards once your hand is empty. After
    playing all face-up cards, you choose a face-down card without knowing what it
    is.\n\nIn the beginning of the game you can\nchange out the face-up cards to
    any \ncard that you have in your hand."
